ttp_template:
<group name="day_hour_minute_second">
  System up time: {{DAY}} day {{HOUR}} hour {{MINUTE}} minute {{SECOND | ORPHRASE}} second
</group>
cli_content: System up time: 11 day 22 hour 5 minute 17 second
textfsm_template:
Value DAY (\d+)
Value HOUR (\d+)
Value MINUTE (\d+)
Value SECOND (\d+)

Start
  ^\s+System\s+up\s+time:\s+${DAY}\s+day\s+${HOUR}\s+hour\s+${MINUTE}\s+minute\s+${SECOND}\s+
  ^\s*$$ -> EOF
  ^. -> Error
